text.section:
The application shall:
Be signed and verified by the applicant; and
Provide the information that the Secretary requires, including:
The name and address of the applicant;
The street address of the property where the private group home is to be located or, if no address, a description which identifies the property;
If the applicant does not own the property, the name of the owner;
A statement that the applicant will comply with the laws, rules, and regulations that relate to the establishing and operating of private group homes under this subtitle;
A statement that the applicant has sufficient resources to establish a private group home, or that those resources are available to the applicant; and
A statement that the applicant's facilities meet the federal regulation requirements on program accessibility (45 C.F.R. §§ 84.21 through 84.23).
